attributes.eligibility:
This resource is for:

-Seniors age 55 and older;
-Disabled individuals;
-Low to moderate income individuals and families with dependent children;
-Emancipated foster youth;
-Veterans;
-Victims of domestic violence or violent crimes; or
-Pregnant women in their second trimester.

You must be homeless and/or have received an eviction notice.

